nodes.text: The Indomitable was an Imperial-class Star Destroyer.

It was constructed at the Kuat Drive Yards shipyards on Kuat in 3 ABY. Shannon Voorson was able to slice its name along with several other Star Destroyer names and gave it to her cousin, Deen Voorson, a member of the Rebel Alliance.
